    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1) featuring the M96.05 3.6L horizontally-opposed six-cylinder engine paired with a crisp G97 6-speed manual transaxle. This example exhibits strong compression across all cylinders and linear power delivery through the VarioCam Plus range. The chassis remains taut with refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the communicative feedback synonymous with the 997's hydraulic steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance includes an upgraded IMS bearing and RMS replacement, mitigating common failure points. The exterior and interior present well, reflecting consistent care and mechanical sympathy. A driver-focused machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
