      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the expected minor road chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is clean and tear-free, though it displays gentle softening in high-traffic areas. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having undergone regular fluid changes and a recent brake service, ensuring a smooth and responsive drive. All electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, function exactly as they should. It is a reliable, attractive choice for a driver who wants a premium experience without the showroom-new price tag. Complete service records are available upon request.",
      "price": 36500.0,
