    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplar of sustained mechanical integrity and refined engineering. This unit has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak operational performance and consistent road composure. Featuring a sophisticated interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers a superior driving experience for the discerning professional. This acquisition represents a strategic investment in quality, providing the prestige of a high-caliber automobile at a calculated market value.",
      "price": 36850.0,
