    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! Honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable ride and it's in really great shape. I've taken good care of it, so it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure with a new owner. It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend trips! If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s been loved, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
