    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, the double VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical upgrade for this chassis. The suspension retains its signature handling balance with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls hard through the entire power band, and the compression ratios remain within factory spec. A well-sorted enthusiast machine ready for the twisties.",
